description:
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a mix of full time and/or part time positions for applicants with an interest in working with people with a range of mental health conditions and older adults in the Liverpool and Sefton area.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Based within Clockview Hospital in Walton and covering across the five wards here, the successful applicants will be working as a key member of the occupational therapy service on the wards. We are looking for self-motivated and caring individuals who can facilitate group activities and assist the qualified occupational therapy staff as required. Hours would primarily be working 9-5pm, but with flexibility at the weekend to facilitate a 7 day service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lee Mutch&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Newton Ward&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;0151 330 7322&lt;/p&gt;
